title: Deer Hunter Tournament
description:
We look forward to bringing you all the latest on the next entry into the biggest hunting videogame franchise of all time. This site will be a home to avid gamers and hunters alike. Come back often to find out why gaming site Kotaku.com says, "Deer Hunter aims to be the most realistic hunting game on the market and from what I saw; they are certainly meeting their goal."

Whether you're here to talk real or digital hunting, there's something here for you. Have a look around!
